text: Rudy Jansen (born 2 January 1979 in Utrecht) is a Dutch former footballer. His former clubs are FC Utrecht, Heracles Almelo, Excelsior, SC Cambuur, FC Zwolle and Spakenburg. ==References== Category:1979 births Category:Living people Category:Footballers from Utrecht (city) Category:Association football defenders Category:Dutch footballers Category:SBV Excelsior players Category:FC Utrecht players Category:Heracles Almelo players Category:SC Cambuur players Category:PEC Zwolle players Category:SV Spakenburg players Category:Eredivisie players Category:Eerste Divisie players
